--- Domain Entities ---
StepAction           enum { RightClick, LeftClick, Switch(SwitchMode) }
SwitchMode           enum { QQ, Num31 } (serde)
SequenceStep         struct { action: StepAction, delay_ms: u32 }
SniperSequence       struct { steps: Vec<SequenceStep> }
Key                  enum { Q, Key1, Key3 }

--- Domain Ports ---
InputEnginePort      trait { right_click(), left_click(), press(Key), release(Key) }
ConfigPort           trait { load(), save() }

--- Listener ---
Linux: evdev non-exclusive read — opens /dev/input/event* without grab
  - Thread per device reads EV_KEY events via channel
  - LeftClick (BTN_LEFT press) when active → execute sequence
  - Toggle key press → flip active state
  - Compositor still receives events normally
Windows/macOS: rdev::listen — X11/WinAPI global hook

--- App Config (TOML) ---
AppConfig            struct {
                       buka_delay_ms: u32 (default 70, 0-100)
                       tembak_delay_ms: u32 (default 30, 0-100)
                       tutup_delay_ms: u32 (default 50, 0-100)
                       ganti_delay_ms: u32 (default 50, 0-100)
                       switch_mode: SwitchMode (default QQ)
                       toggle_key: String (default "F12")
                     }

--- App State (runtime) ---
AppState             struct {
                       active: AtomicBool
                       config: Mutex<AppConfig>
                     }
